OL,9,FStaff at a popular cafe are warning
OL,10,Fother businesses to be vigilant after
OL,11,Fdiners racked up a large bill and then
OL,12,Fleft without paying.
OL,14,FThe 'dine and dash' approach to eating
OL,15,Fout is becoming increasingly common,
OL,16,Faccording to experts in the
OL,17,Fhospitality industry.
