OL,3,CMan and two children flee independent
OL,4,Ccafe without paying large bill
OL,6,FFootage from Cafe No.35 in
OL,7,FCanterbury's St Margret's Street shows
OL,8,Fa man, with two children sitting
OL,9,Foutside, enjoying two fried breakfasts
OL,10,Falong with three portion of chips,
OL,11,Ffive cokes and a milkshake.
OL,13,FThe CCTV captures the gentleman
OL,14,Frepeatedly staring inside as he
OL,15,Frequested more food from the menu.
OL,17,F"They sat out here and he kept looking
OL,18,Fthrough the window and just ordering
OL,19,Fmore and more food and he started to
OL,20,Fget suspicious", says business owner
OL,21,FAnna Carpenter.
OL,26,@lD@DrrnD@Qrr
