OL,3,CMan and two children flee independent
OL,4,Ccafe without paying large bill
OL,6,F"I think they were trying to see how
OL,7,Fwe do things here and to work out when
OL,8,Fwould be a good time to leave without
OL,9,Fpaying."
OL,11,FAfter going inside to the counter and
OL,12,Fordering more food, with staff out the
OL,13,Fback, the three then briskly left the
OL,14,Frestaurant without paying the bill
OL,15,Fwhich was just over #50.
OL,17,FAnna added, "It's a loss to us.
OL,18,FEverything we produce here has a cost
OL,19,Fto it. We're very appreciative of all
OL,20,Fthe customers that support us.
OL,26,@lD@Drr
