OL,6,F"So when somebody comes along and
OL,7,Fbasically steals from us it has an
OL,8,Fimpact on the business, it has an
OL,9,Fimpact on me personally and an impact
OL,10,Fon the staff.
OL,12,F"It certainly seems to be on the
OL,13,Fincrease. There's lots of independent
OL,14,Fbusinesses in Canterbury that are
OL,15,Ftrying to keep going in a very
OL,16,Fdifficult."
OL,18,FMore reports are being received of
OL,19,Fpeople leaving without paying, with
OL,20,Findustry bodies urging businesses to
OL,21,Freport any such incidents to police.
