OL,6,FA restaurant in Hastings reported 12
OL,7,Fpeople eating at her restaurant before
OL,8,Fleaving a #400 bill behind them.
OL,10,FA UK Hospitality spokesperson said,
OL,11,F"Any customers walking out of
OL,12,Frestaurants without paying is simply
OL,13,Funacceptable and shows a complete lack
OL,14,Fof respect towards businesses and
OL,15,Fteams that work incredibly hard to
OL,16,Fprovide guests with good service, good
OL,17,Ffood and good experiences.
OL,19,F"We would encourage any operators who
OL,20,Fexperience walkouts to report it to
OL,21,Fthe police."
